divs: Sighting DetailsAbout 6 lights in a triangle shape evenly spaced. Appeared to be one craft. Hovered about 200 feet off the ground, hovered over local farm field above Hwy 164 and skyline Ave for approximately 3 minutes with extremely quiet jet engine sound. No rotor thump of that of a helicopter. I drove under it and it slowly flew away at about 30 mph, with no engine increase in sound. Clear night sky but I could not get a clear visual of the craft.
